data.description: Discover the epitome of modern living in this beautiful 2 story, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home! The granite countertops, stylish island, and updated countertops elevate the kitchen. Enjoy the plush feel of the carpet and luxury vinyl floors throughout the home. The double vanity bathrooms, walk-in closets, and spacious laundry radiates convenience. A fenced backyard gives you privacy and peace. Welcome home to comfort, style, and a neighborhood you'll love!
